            <title>[FELIX-4486] Possible thread leakage in DA</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4486</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the DA starts the installation of a DP, it will start a thread to copy the contents of the input stream to persist the DP while installing it. When the installation fails before anything is actually installed, this thread is not properly closed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
